values.comment: A subset of a coded or non coded list of values.

values.comment: A single unique serial number which identifies shipping containers or shipping packages.

values.label: Case number

values.label: Financial security identification number
values.comment: Identification number of a financial security.

values.label: Compact disk player security code number

values.label: Question in questionnaire

values.label: Questionnaire
values.comment: The identification of a questionnaire.

values.label: Check digit
values.comment: The check digit of the primary number.

values.label: Vehicle telephone identification number

values.label: Door key number

values.label: Ignition key number
values.comment: The number on the key that fits the ignition lock.

values.label: Radio security code number
values.comment: The security code number of the radio.

values.label: Fleet vehicle unit number
values.comment: The unit number of the vehicle within the fleet allocated by the fleet operator.

values.label: Vehicle registration number
values.comment: The registration number of the vehicle.

values.label: Accounting Classification Reference Number (ACRN)
values.comment: A reference number identifying the accounting classification.

values.label: Serial number

values.label: Fund

values.label: Special Accounting Classification Reference Number (ACRN)
values.comment: A reference number identifying a special accounting classification.

values.label: Project
values.comment: A code identifying a project.

values.label: Transportation Account Code (TAC)
values.comment: A code identifying a transportation account.

values.label: Financial details
values.comment: A code identifying financial details for accounting.

values.label: Account manager
values.comment: A code identifying the account manager.

values.label: Package buyer assigned identifier
values.comment: [1438] Unique number allocated by the buyer to identify an individual package.

values.label: Successor constraint
values.comment: Identity number is a successor constraint.

values.label: Batch number

values.comment: The identity number of a health-care professional.

values.comment: The identity number of a public institution.

values.label: Link set
values.comment: The identity number of a set of links.

values.label: Organisation chart

values.comment: A unique identifier assigned to an insurer.

values.label: Hospital issued healthcare provider number
values.comment: Identity number of a healthcare service provider issued by a hospital.

values.label: Healthcare practice identification number
values.comment: Uniquely identifies the practice in which one or more healthcare providers conduct business.

values.label: Agent identification number
values.comment: A unique identifier assigned to an agent.

values.label: Insurer group identification number
values.comment: The identification number of the insurer's group.

values.label: Chassis number
values.comment: Unique number affixed by manufacturer to a chassis for identification purposes.

values.label: Invoice number
values.comment: Number assigned to the invoice.

values.label: Account number
values.comment: Account identification number.

values.label: Internal control number
values.comment: Control number assigned for internal use.

values.label: Policy number
values.comment: Number uniquely identifying a policy.

values.label: Attribute set
values.comment: A set of attributes.

values.label: Footnote set
values.comment: A set of footnotes.

values.label: GS1 Global Individual Asset Identifier
values.comment: Unique number, consisting of the GS1 Company Prefix and an Individual Asset Reference.

values.label: Legband
values.comment: A band attached to the leg of a live animal to uniquely identify the animal.

values.label: Authority registered number
values.comment: A number registered by an authority to identify a particular commodity or goods.

values.label: Identification tag, affixed
values.comment: An identification tag affixed to a commodity or goods, e.g. livestock.

values.label: Identification tattoo
values.comment: A tattooed identification, e.g. on livestock.

values.label: Identification wingband
values.comment: An identification band attached to the wing of a bird.

values.label: GS1 Global Returnable Asset Identifier, without serial number
values.comment: A unique number, consisting of a fixed 13-digits part. It allows the unique identification of a particular type of Returnable Asset.

values.label: GS1 Global Returnable Asset Identifier, with serial number
values.comment: A unique number, consisting of a fixed 13-digits part and a mandatory Serial Number of up to 16 digits. The fixed part allows for the unique identification of a particular kind of Returnable Asset, the second part is assigned to distinguish individual assets within a given Returnable Asset type.

values.label: GS1 Global Identification Number for Consignment (GINC)
values.comment: A unique number that identify a consignment comprised of one or more logistic units that are intended to be transported together.

values.label: GS1 Global Shipment Identification Number (GSIN)
values.comment: A unique number that identify a shipment comprised of one or more logistic units that are intended to be delivered together.

values.label: Engine number
values.comment: Unique number affixed by manufacturer to an engine for identification purposes.

values.label: Coupon number
values.comment: A number identifying a coupon which is attached to the identified product.

values.label: Cheque number
values.comment: A number identifying a cheque.

values.label: GS1 Global Trade Item Number (GTIN)
values.comment: A unique number, up to 14-digits, assigned according to the numbering structure of the GS1 system, to identify a trade item.

values.label: IMEI code
values.comment: The International Mobile Station Equipment Identity (IMEI) is a unique number to identify mobile phones. It includes the origin, model and serial number of the device. The structure is specified in 3GPP TS 23.003.

values.label: Emulsion number
values.comment: Manufacturer assigned reference to a photographic product indicating sensitivity.

values.label: Invoice line number
values.comment: Sequential numerical assignment to identical invoiced goods which are subject to the same conditions of sale.

values.label: Marking/label number
values.comment: The number on the marking or label.

values.label: Part number
values.comment: Manufacturer-assigned reference to a product part.

values.label: Secondary Customs tariff number
values.comment: Indicate (e.g. in segment GIR) the secondary (sub-) level of a Customs tariff number.

values.label: Vehicle identity number
values.comment: Unique serial number assigned by the manufacturer that distinguishes one vehicle from another.

values.label: Skid number
values.comment: A number identifying a skid or pallet.

values.label: Authorisation
values.comment: Official approval.

values.label: Insurance policy
values.comment: Contract of insurance.

values.label: Transport unit identification according to ISO/IEC 15459
values.comment: The identification of a transport unit according to ISO/IEC 15459 (ISO: International Organization for Standardization. IEC: International Electrotechnical Commission).

values.label: Indivisible transport unit according to ISO/IEC 15459
values.comment: The identification of an indivisible transport unit according to ISO/IEC 15459 (ISO: International Organization for Standardization. IEC: International Electrotechnical Commission).

values.label: Divisible transport unit according to ISO/IEC 15459
values.comment: The identification of a divisible transport unit according to ISO/IEC 15459 (ISO: International Organization for Standardization. IEC: International Electrotechnical Commission).
